  <brief_title>The Safety and Efficacy of Naltrexone and Scopolamine Utilized in the Treatment of Major Depression</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Safety and Efficacy of Naltrexone and Scopolamine Utilized in Combination in the Treatment of Major Depression: A Double Blinded, Randomized, Controlled Pilot Study</official_title>
